TITLE: fy_killzone_day
AUTHORS: warflango, MashedChicken
E-MAIL: redantlioncult@gmail.com

FILENAME: fy_killzone_day.bsp
FILESIZE: 2.93 MB
DATE RELEASED: 2/25/07

CREDITS: Credits to Valve for all textures, models, etc. and to the Valve Developer wiki for tutorials, etc.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Drag the maps folder in this zip into your Counter-Strike Source directory (i.e. C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\<your account name>\counter-strike source\).

DESCRIPTION: A Counter-Strike Source map based around two forts and a series of trenches and tunnels between them.

COMMENTS: This map is a variant of the map fy_killzone made by the same authors.

Reskinned by MashedChicken for the daytime.
